Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你真是爛透了， 湯姆\N{\rDefault}You're a jerk, Thom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,聽著希莉亞， 我們必須順著我們的感覺走\N{\rDefault}Look Celia, we have to follow our passions;
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 你熱愛機械工學， 而我只是想去太空中耍帥一下\N{\rDefault}...you have your robotics, and I just want to be awesome in space.
