Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我沒有害怕， 只是...\N{\rDefault}I'm not freaked out by- it's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 好好好！\N{\rDefault}...alright! Fine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我承認 我被嚇傻了！ 我還做惡夢被它追著跑...\N{\rDefault}I'm freaked out! I have nightmares that I'm being chased...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 被這些巨大的奪命機器爪子追殺...\N{\rDefault}...by these giant robotic claws of death...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.20,0:00:45.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,隨便你怎麼說。 湯姆， 我們之間玩完了\N{\rDefault}"Fourty years later" Whatever, Thom. We're done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.00,0:00:53.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,機器人記憶同步鎖定完成！\N{\rDefault}Robot's memory synced and locked!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.00,0:01:03.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,這個挺詭異的\N{\rDefault}This is pretty freaky.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你是不是該下去了吧？\N{\rDefault}Shouldn't you be down there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我昨天聽到你們這些傢伙的談話\N{\rDefault}I heard you guys talking last night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你知道的， 這不是我的錯\N{\rDefault}It's not my fault, you know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎？\N{\rDefault}Are you ready?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你當然準備好了， 你是個搖滾明星嘛\N{\rDefault}Of course you're ready, you're a rockstar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,情況如何， 貝里？\N{\rDefault}How's it looking, Barley?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我們應該有10分鐘左右的時間...\N{\rDefault}We should have about ten minutes...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,好的， 棒極了\N{\rDefault}Well that's perfect.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,一分鐘後開始！ 全部的系統啟動！ 對， 你也是， 快點！\N{\rDefault}We're on in one! All systems go! Yeah you, go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:32.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,快！ 動起來！ 快快快！\N{\rDefault}Go! Move your asses! Go go go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.00,0:03:37.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,這個我喜歡！ 拜託， 快！\N{\rDefault}I love it! Come on, go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rDefault}That's nice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.70,Default_1,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好擔心的\N{\rDefault}Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,湯姆\N{\rDefault}Thom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,她在那\N{\rDefault}There she is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,就是現在\N{\rDefault}Now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你是愛她的\N{\rDefault}You love her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,她就是你的熱情\N{\rDefault}She is your passion!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,溫柔點\N{\rDefault}Be tender to her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,要誠懇！ 溫柔些\N{\rDefault}Be honest! Eh- be tender.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,讓她回憶起什麼是愛\N{\rDefault}Remind her what love is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 好， 開演！\N{\rDefault}...and, action!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,記憶覆寫開始！\N{\rDefault}Memory overwrite in progress!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你真是爛透了， 湯姆！\N{\rDefault}You're a jerk, Thom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,噢， 抱歉， 不好意思\N{\rDefault}Ohp- Sorry! Sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,聽著， 希莉亞\N{\rDefault}Look Celia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我們必須順著我們的感覺走\N{\rDefault}We have to follow our passions.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你熱愛機械工學...\N{\rDefault}You have your robotics...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 而我只是想去太空中耍帥一下\N{\rDefault}...and I just want to be awesome in space.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,好的， 它們來了。 還有兩分鐘！\N{\rDefault}Okay, they're coming. Two minutes left!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,快點， 湯姆！\N{\rDefault}Speed it up, Thom!
