Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不肯承認被我的機械手臂嚇壞了？\N{\rDefault}Why don't you just admit that you're freaked out by my robot hand?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,聽著， 希莉亞， 我那時還年輕...\N{\rDefault}Listen Celia, I was young...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 只是個小屁孩\N{\rDefault}...and a dick.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,但是這不是毀滅這個世界的理由\N{\rDefault}But that's no reason to destroy the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,他為啥要這麼說？\N{\rDefault}Why does he do this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我們已經試過這個情景了！\N{\rDefault}We already tried that one!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,中止！\N{\rDefault}Abort!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,停！\N{\rDefault}Cut!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,噢啊啊啊！\N{\rDefault}Whoaaa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,噢啊啊啊！\N{\rDefault}Whoaaa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,不...\N{\rDefault}Nooooo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你傷透了我的心\N{\rDefault}You broke my heart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rDefault}I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你把我拋棄在地球上\N{\rDefault}You forgot me on earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rDefault}I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我應該把你碎屍萬段\N{\rDefault}I should just crush you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,對...\N{\rDefault}I'm-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rDefault}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,說的很自然\N{\rDefault}Good ad-lib.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,這不是我的錯！\N{\rDefault}Not my fault!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,這次\N{\rDefault}This time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.50,Default_1,,0,0,0,,上面安靜點！\N{\rDefault}Quiet on set!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我們沒時間了！\N{\rDefault}We're out of time!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,快點！\N{\rDefault}Come on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,啊...\N{\rDefault}RAAAAAAAAH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,記憶覆寫， 90%\N{\rDefault}Memory overwrite, 90%.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,隊長！ 我們必須放棄了！\N{\rDefault}Captain! We have to abort!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,這個世界已經不一樣了， 希莉亞...\N{\rDefault}The world's changed, Celia...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,... 或許， 我們也可以改變\N{\rDefault}...maybe we can too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,記憶覆寫完成！\N{\rDefault}Memory overwrite complete!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎\N{\rDefault}You know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.00,Default_1,,0,0,0,,我們可以從中學到一課\N{\rDefault}There's a lesson to be learned from this.
